chart_description: This chart shows the percentage of memory utilization where some pressure exists. This indicates there are some memory constraints and usage is more than usual but not critical yet.

dimension_descriptions.some 10: This dimension shows the memory some pressure at 10-second intervals.
dimension_descriptions.some 300: This dimension shows the memory some pressure at 5 minute intervals.
dimension_descriptions.some 60: This dimension shows the memory some pressure at 1 minute intervals.
